// CSharpCodeAnalyst rules

DENY CSharpCodeAnalyst.Analyzers.** -> CSharpCodeAnalyst.**

// The application is only allowed to instantiate the anlyzers
DENY CSharpCodeAnalyst.** -> CSharpCodeAnalyst.Analyzers.**
ALLOW CSharpCodeAnalyst.** -> CSharpCodeAnalyst.Analyzers.CSharpCodeAnalyst.Analyzers.ArchitecturalRules.Analyzer.*
ALLOW CSharpCodeAnalyst.** -> CSharpCodeAnalyst.Analyzers.CSharpCodeAnalyst.Analyzers.ArchitecturalRules.Violation.*
ALLOW CSharpCodeAnalyst.** -> CSharpCodeAnalyst.Analyzers.CSharpCodeAnalyst.Analyzers.ArchitecturalRules.ViolationsFormatter.*
ALLOW CSharpCodeAnalyst.** -> CSharpCodeAnalyst.Analyzers.CSharpCodeAnalyst.Analyzers.EventRegistration.Analyzer.*
ALLOW CSharpCodeAnalyst.** -> CSharpCodeAnalyst.Analyzers.CSharpCodeAnalyst.Analyzers.MethodComplexity.Analyzer.*
ALLOW CSharpCodeAnalyst.** -> CSharpCodeAnalyst.Analyzers.CSharpCodeAnalyst.Analyzers.TypeCohesion.Analyzer.*
ALLOW CSharpCodeAnalyst.** -> CSharpCodeAnalyst.Analyzers.CSharpCodeAnalyst.Analyzers.TypeDependencies.Analyzer.*

// The Sdk can only access the CodeGraph
RESTRICT CSharpCodeAnalyst.AnalyzerSdk.** -> CSharpCodeAnalyst.CodeGraph.**

// CodeParser can only access the CodeGraph
RESTRICT CSharpCodeAnalyst.CodeParser.** -> CSharpCodeAnalyst.CodeGraph.**

// CodeGraph is at the bottom, only incoming edges
DENY CSharpCodeAnalyst.CodeGraph.** -> CSharpCodeAnalyst.CodeParser.**
DENY CSharpCodeAnalyst.CodeGraph.** -> CSharpCodeAnalyst.AnalyzerSdk.**
DENY CSharpCodeAnalyst.CodeGraph.** -> CSharpCodeAnalyst.Analyzers.**
DENY CSharpCodeAnalyst.CodeGraph.** -> CSharpCodeAnalyst.**

